      /*

parameterised ML table of best model fit for subj vs. obj prob

11/01/2013 Markus Schaffner

*/

clear all
set more off

cd /Users/schaffne/Dropbox/OET
use "oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta", clear

do oet_first_paper/do/varsets.do


// Conditional Invariant Prelect(1998) 
program define OET_ML4
args lnf sigma beta gamma eta
tempvar j
gen double `j'=`gamma'*exp(-`beta'*(1-winpc^`eta')/`eta')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end

local vars1 = "$minimal"
local vars2 = ""

ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:pse= `vars1' `vars2') (beta4: `vars1' `vars2') (gamma4:  `vars1' `vars2') (eta4: ) 
// ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
// ml graph
estimates store m5a


local vars1 = "$minimal $exp"

ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:pse= `vars1' `vars2') (beta4: `vars1' `vars2') (gamma4:  `vars1' `vars2') (eta4: ) 
// ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
// ml graph
estimates store m5c

local vars2 = "$demo $edu "

ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:pse= `vars1' `vars2') (beta4: `vars1' `vars2') (gamma4:  `vars1' `vars2') (eta4: ) 
// ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
// ml graph
estimates store m5d

local vars2 = "$demo $edu $psych $phycho"

ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:pse= `vars1' `vars2') (beta4: `vars1' `vars2') (gamma4:  `vars1' `vars2') (eta4: ) 
// ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
// ml graph
estimates store m5e


estout * using oet_first_paper/tables/paramML.tex, style(tex) replace ///
   cells( "b(fmt(%9.3fc) star vacant(&)) se(fmt(%9.3fc) par)" ) ///
   label ///
   mlabels(none) ///
   collabels(none) ///
   eqlabels( " \textbf{$\sigma$}"  "  \hline\hline  \textbf{$\beta$}"  "  \hline\hline \textbf{$\gamma$}"  "  \hline\hline  \textbf{$\eta$}") ///
   stats(N ll, fmt( %9.0f %9.3f) labels("\$N$" "\$ll$") layout( \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} \multicolumn{2}{c}{@} ) ) ///
   varlabels( sigma:_cons "constant" beta4:_cons "constant" gamma4:_cons "constant" eta4:_cons "constant" ) ///
   prefoot("\hline") ///
   starlevels("&" 1.00 "&*" 0.10 "&**" 0.05 "&***" 0.01)
